The paper deals with mechanisms for candidate selection and minimizing social cost, which are topics in game theory (cs.GT) and data structures (cs.DS). The use of metric spaces and optimization also suggests categories such as artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
